name: Crypto Icons #29
description: A sleek cryptocurrency visualization featuring glowing icons of Ethereum (blue), Bitcoin (orange), and Dogecoin (gold) against a dark background with a circuit board grid pattern. The design includes three stylized price charts at the bottom showing the relative performance of each cryptocurrency, while decorative binary code in the corners adds a digital aesthetic to this financial technology themed composition.

attributes.value: Dark with Blue, Orange, Gold Accents
